---
title: Parallel Execution - Stage 3 & 4
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Pipeline
    participant T as Thread 1: Transcriber
    participant D as Thread 2: Diarizer
    participant Cache as Cache Layer

    P->>P: Split audio → chunks
    
    rect rgb(220, 252, 231)
    Note over P,D: ⚡ PARALLEL EXECUTION (ThreadPoolExecutor)
    par
        P->>T: transcribe_all(chunks)
        P->>D: run_diarization(chunks)
    end
    end

    loop per chunk
        T->>Cache: Check cache (MD5)
        alt Cache HIT
            Cache-->>T: Load cached transcript
        else Cache MISS
            T->>T: Whisper / AssemblyAI
            T->>Cache: Save to cache
        end
    end

    loop per chunk
        D->>Cache: Check cache (MD5)
        alt Cache HIT
            Cache-->>D: Load cached diarization
        else Cache MISS
            D->>D: Pyannote / SpeechBrain / VAD
            D->>Cache: Save to cache
        end
    end

    P->>P: merge_transcript_with_diarization()
    Note over P: Fallback ke sequential jika paralel gagal
